This project uses py.test for its tests.

Install it with apt install python3-pytest

To run the tests from the root of the git repository:

$ python3 -m pytest

or just:

$ py.test-3

For coverage information install the pytest-cov plugin with:

$ pip3 install --user pytest-cov

And run:

$ py.test-3 --cov=en16931

For information on the missing statements:

$ py.test-3 --cov-report term-missing --cov=en16931
